# Code Owners for SkunkLabz GitHub Runner Images
#
# This file defines who should be automatically requested for review
# when changes are made to specific files or directories.
#
# Order is important; the last matching pattern takes the most precedence.

# Global fallback - all files
* @skunklabz

# Core build and deployment files
dockerfiles/ @skunklabz
